				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${{\rm{TL}}}_{{\rm{i}}}={\rm{\Sigma }}({{\rm{TL}}}_{{\rm{j}}}\ast {{\rm{Dc}}}_{{\rm{ij}}})$$\end{document}TLi=Σ(TLj∗Dcij)where TLj is the fractional trophic level of species j (prey), and DCij is the fraction of j in diet i28.

